extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Courses:] !{data.c_count}
      li #[strong Users:] !{data.u_count}
      li #[strong Exams:] !{data.e_count}
      li #[strong Universities:] !{data.un_count}
      li #[strong Papers:] !{data.p_count}